---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
import VideoEmbed from '../../components/VideoEmbed.astro';
import { BUSINESS } from '../../consts';

import educationHero from '../../assets/education-hero.jpg';
import classroom from '../../assets/education-classroom.jpg';
import educationBenefits from '../../assets/education-benefits.png';

/*
 * 1:1 reproduction of the live gsuair.com Education page: same heading, same
 * copy, same order, same links — nothing added, nothing removed. That includes
 * the trailing editor note by the video, kept at the owner's request.
 */
---

<Base
  title="Education"
  description="Poor indoor air quality in schools has been linked to drowsiness, headaches, loss of concentration, and asthma. ActivePure® has a solution to meet your facilities' unique needs."
>
  <PageHero
    title="IMPROVING STUDENT PRODUCTIVITY & REDUCING ABSENTEEISM!"
    image={educationHero}
    imageAlt="Brick school building on a sunny day"
  >
    <p class="mt-6">
      <a
        href={`tel:${BUSINESS.phoneHref}`}
        class="text-lg font-semibold text-white underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-accent-400"
      >
        {BUSINESS.phone}
      </a>
    </p>
  </PageHero>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <Section tone="tint">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr]">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        <p>
          Poor indoor air quality affects the health of each of us. For children, it can affect their neurodevelopment
          and cognitive ability negatively.
        </p>
        <p>
          Indoor air quality problems in schools have been linked to drowsiness, headaches, loss of concentration, and
          asthma. It also increases absenteeism and leads to children falling behind academically. Additionally, class
          sizes that are predetermined by state boards of education make it more difficult to distance one child from
          another.
        </p>
      </div>
      <Image
        src={classroom}
        alt="Students raising their hands in a classroom"
        widths={[400, 700, 1000]}
        sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 26rem, 100vw"
        class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- A solution for every school -->
  <Section tone="brand">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-brand-100">
      <p>
        Whether you need clean air in K-12 schools, elementary or primary schools, secondary schools, colleges,
        universities, trade schools or an entire school district, ActivePure® has a solution to meet your facilities'
        unique needs.
      </p>
      <p>
        The system does not just purify the air, it sanitizes all surfaces. HVAC-installed units as well as portables
        allow each school to customize a system to meet its specific needs. In older school buildings with poor
        ventilation, portable units can get to work immediately to sanitize exposed surfaces and the air in occupied
        spaces without the cost of overhauling an HVAC system. A school can simply place an ActivePure® unit in each
        classroom, plugging it into a regular wall outlet. It is that easy.
      </p>
      <p>
        The system includes marketing materials to promote your investment in your school and educate your team members,
        educators, students, and parents about the benefits for all.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!--
    "System benefits" graphic, as on the live page. Its bullet text exists only
    inside the pixels, so it is transcribed into alt text rather than re-typed
    as body copy — the live page has no text equivalent.
  -->
  <Section tone="tint">
    <Image
      src={educationBenefits}
      alt="System benefits: the #1 ranked continuous air purification system capable of attacking COVID-19 in the air and on surfaces immediately; reduces almost 100% of surface and airborne contaminants within the first 24 hours of use; controls and neutralizes contaminants such as viruses, bacteria, mold, fungi and VOC in real-time; the technology releases ActivePure® molecules which allows the neutralization of pathogens and contaminants on impact; minimal maintenance; ultra-quiet; cost-effective; installed and portable solutions available."
      widths={[400, 600, 864]}
      sizes="(min-width: 640px) 26rem, 90vw"
      class="mx-auto w-full max-w-md rounded-lg shadow-md"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </Section>

  <!-- Grants & Funding -->
  <Section tone="tint">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
      <p>
        Grants &amp; Funding are available for educational facilities. Navigate to our{' '}
        <a href="/funding" class="font-bold text-brand-700 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-brand-600">
          Funding Page
        </a>{' '}
        and contact us anytime for more information. We are happy to help you decide which air purification system is
        best for your school facility.
      </p>
      <p>
        GERM SOLUTIONS USA believes that school administrators, teachers, staff members, and children have the right to
        get an education in a clean-air learning environment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- School video -->
  <Section tone="brand" align="center">
    <p class="mb-10 text-center text-lg leading-relaxed text-brand-100">
      If we have a school video IF NOT A TESTIMONIAL
    </p>
    <VideoEmbed src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6eXyTL8-2_A" title="School video" />
  </Section>
</Base>
